#: ../../user/changelog.md:9
msgid ""
"Mock call-argument matchers: `toHaveBeenCalledWith`, "
"`toHaveBeenLastCalledWith`, `toHaveBeenNthCalledWith`, "
"`toHaveBeenCalledExactlyOnceWith` (each with a two-argument `…With2` "
"variant)."
msgstr ""
"モックの呼び出し引数マッチャー: "
"`toHaveBeenCalledWith`、`toHaveBeenLastCalledWith`、`toHaveBeenNthCalledWith`、`toHaveBeenCalledExactlyOnceWith`（それぞれ"
" 2 引数版 `…With2` を含む）。"

#: ../../user/changelog.md:10
msgid ""
"Mock return-value matchers: `toHaveReturnedTimes`, `toHaveReturnedWith`, "
"`toHaveLastReturnedWith`, `toHaveNthReturnedWith`."
msgstr ""
"モックの返り値マッチャー: "
"`toHaveReturnedTimes`、`toHaveReturnedWith`、`toHaveLastReturnedWith`、`toHaveNthReturnedWith`。"

#: ../../user/changelog.md:11
msgid ""
"`Vi.MockFn` lifecycle helpers: `mockResolvedValueOnce`, "
"`mockRejectedValueOnce`, `mockReturnThis`, `getMockName`, `mockName`, "
"`getMockImplementation`, `withImplementation`."
msgstr ""
"`Vi.MockFn` のライフサイクルヘルパー: "
"`mockResolvedValueOnce`、`mockRejectedValueOnce`、`mockReturnThis`、`getMockName`、`mockName`、`getMockImplementation`、`withImplementation`。"

#: ../../user/changelog.md:12
msgid ""
"`Vi` mock inspection and hoisting helpers: `mocked`, `isMockFunction`, "
"`hoisted`."
msgstr "`Vi` のモック検査・ホイストヘルパー: `mocked`、`isMockFunction`、`hoisted`。"

#: ../../user/changelog.md:13
msgid ""
"Per-test lifecycle hooks: `onTestFailed`, `onTestFinished` (each with an "
"`…Async` variant)."
msgstr "テスト単位のライフサイクルフック: `onTestFailed`、`onTestFinished`（それぞれ `…Async` バリアントを含む）。"

#: ../../user/changelog.md:14
msgid ""
"Type and predicate matchers: `toBeTypeOf`, `toBeInstanceOf`, `toBeOneOf`,"
" `toSatisfy`."
msgstr "型・述語マッチャー: `toBeTypeOf`、`toBeInstanceOf`、`toBeOneOf`、`toSatisfy`。"

#: ../../user/changelog.md:15
msgid ""
"Async-mock resolve matchers: `toHaveResolved`, `toHaveResolvedTimes`, "
"`toHaveResolvedWith`, `toHaveLastResolvedWith`, `toHaveNthResolvedWith`."
msgstr ""
"async モックの resolve マッチャー: "
"`toHaveResolved`、`toHaveResolvedTimes`、`toHaveResolvedWith`、`toHaveLastResolvedWith`、`toHaveNthResolvedWith`。"

#: ../../user/changelog.md:16
msgid ""
"Async fake timers: `advanceTimersByTimeAsync`, `runAllTimersAsync`, "
"`runOnlyPendingTimersAsync`, `advanceTimersToNextTimerAsync`, "
"`advanceTimersToNextFrame`."
msgstr ""
"async フェイクタイマー: "
"`advanceTimersByTimeAsync`、`runAllTimersAsync`、`runOnlyPendingTimersAsync`、`advanceTimersToNextTimerAsync`、`advanceTimersToNextFrame`。"

#: ../../user/changelog.md:17
msgid ""
"Timer inspection: `isFakeTimers`, `getTimerCount`, `getMockedSystemTime`,"
" `getRealSystemTime`."
msgstr ""
"タイマー検査: "
"`isFakeTimers`、`getTimerCount`、`getMockedSystemTime`、`getRealSystemTime`。"

#: ../../user/changelog.md:18
msgid "Waiting utilities: `waitFor`, `waitUntil`."
msgstr "待機ユーティリティ: `waitFor`、`waitUntil`。"

#: ../../user/changelog.md:19
msgid "Accessor spies: `spyOnGetter`, `spyOnSetter`."
msgstr "アクセサスパイ: `spyOnGetter`、`spyOnSetter`。"

#: ../../user/changelog.md:20
msgid ""
"Global and environment stubs: `stubGlobal`, `stubEnv`, "
"`unstubAllGlobals`, `unstubAllEnvs`."
msgstr "グローバル・環境スタブ: `stubGlobal`、`stubEnv`、`unstubAllGlobals`、`unstubAllEnvs`。"

#: ../../user/changelog.md:21
msgid ""
"Module mocking completion: `importActual`, `importMock`, `doUnmock`, "
"`mockObject`, `dynamicImportSettled`."
msgstr ""
"モジュールモックの補完: "
"`importActual`、`importMock`、`doUnmock`、`mockObject`、`dynamicImportSettled`。"

#: ../../user/changelog.md:22
msgid ""
"Test modifiers: `testSkipIf`, `testRunIf`, `testFails`, `testFailsAsync`,"
" `testSequential`, `testSequentialAsync`."
msgstr ""
"test 修飾子: `testSkipIf`、`testRunIf`、`testFails`、`testFailsAsync`、"
"`testSequential`、`testSequentialAsync`。"

#: ../../user/changelog.md:23
msgid ""
"Describe modifiers: `describeTodo`, `describeConcurrent`, "
"`describeSequential`, `describeShuffle`, `describeSkipIf`, "
"`describeRunIf`, `describeFor`."
msgstr ""
"describe 修飾子: `describeTodo`、`describeConcurrent`、"
"`describeSequential`、`describeShuffle`、`describeSkipIf`、"
"`describeRunIf`、`describeFor`。"

